headline: While Nvidia Drifts, This Trio's Swift Gains Beat S&P 500
summary: While megacap Nvidia has been moving sideways since October, three cruise stocks, including Carnival, have rallied after strong breakouts.  The Investor's Business Daily's Stock Screener also shows that the trio (Carnival has two types of stock) has relative strength lines at a new highs.  Carnival holds a Relative Strength Rating of 94 and its Composite Rating is an ideal 99.
